version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-03-31"
abstract: >-
  A faithful, reproducible, and extensible reference implementation of TurboQuant
  for KV-cache quantization, including MSE and inner-product paths, synthetic
  benchmarks, and a self-contained HTML visual report.
preferred-citation:
  type: article
  title: "TurboQuant: An Efficient and Accurate KV Cache Quantization Method"
  url: "https://arxiv.org/html/2504.19874v1"
